posting_body: ['Property Address', '3000 W River Pkwy S - 207 | Minneapolis, MN 55406', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Available 10/1: Classic one-bedroom apartment across from the Mississippi River!', 'This south-facing apartment features unique cork floors and a rare fireplace.', 'Large windows and a private balcony allow for a lush view of our tall river oaks!', 'This apartment has a mix of classic and contemporary fixtures with original cabinetry and updated lighting.', 'Live in the Longfellow neighborhood located along the beautiful Mississippi River Valley.', 'These beautiful one-bedroom apartments feature sunken living rooms, sunrooms, balconies, walk-out patios, and amazing river views.', 'River Gates is green!', 'The rooftop solar garden has saved over 63k pounds of CO2 emissions to date.', 'See the stats at <URL>!', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Final price subject to change pending walk-through inspection.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 650', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,095.00', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
